{{#is_alert}}

## What's happening?
Connection backpressure on NiFi host {{host.name}} has exceeded 80% for connection {{connection_name.name}}.

At 100%, the upstream processor will be forced to stop. Investigate:
- Whether the downstream processor is running and healthy
- Whether the backpressure threshold needs to be increased
- Whether the downstream processor needs more concurrent tasks

{{/is_alert}}

{{#is_warning}}
Connection backpressure on {{host.name}} for {{connection_name.name}} has exceeded 60%.
{{/is_warning}}

{{#is_recovery}}
Connection backpressure on {{host.name}} for {{connection_name.name}} has returned to normal.
{{/is_recovery}}
